{"tid":1298479,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國傳媒稱北京在修訂逃犯條例讓步，但允香港政改機會微","createTime":"2019-07-09T01:45:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-11T10:18:43.000Z","uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":27,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"b1fff60feed87529abe6413e5270c6c6ca4d96f9","tid":1298479,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T01:45:33.000Z","msg":"source: <a href=\"http://www.metroradio.com.hk/news/live.aspx?NewsID=20190709081238\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.metroradio.com.hk%2Fnews%2Flive.aspx%3FNewsID%3D20190709081238&d=Xf5vvBv8GY7fsWMyNBE0dpBhszO9bAnYmyMPTpIehd8%3D&h=20359374\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.metroradio.com.hk/news/live.aspx?NewsID=20190709081238</a><br />\n<br />\n紐約時報報道, 香港所謂「反送中」的反對修訂逃犯條例事件, 是示威者宣洩雨傘運動失敗5年來的憤怒, 但北京政府已在修訂逃犯條例上讓步, 同意香港政治改革的機會渺茫.<br />\n<br />\n港府推動修訂逃犯條例, 6月兩度激發過百萬人上街抗議, 示威者訴求明確, 包括撤回修例,及調查6月12日在立法會外警方處理示威場面的手法, 是否濫權.<br />\n<br />\n報道指出, 示威者最新訴求, 令香港和內地的關係日益緊張. 為宣洩不滿, 以年輕人為主的示威者闖入立法會, 掀起波瀾, 連親北京的建制派人士, 近日也呼籲港府重啟政治改革.<br />\n<br />\n不過, 報道引述專家的意見表示, <span style=\"color: red;\">中共總書記習近平在2012年掌權以來</span>, 加強控制全國, 今次容許行政長官林鄭月娥暫緩修例, <span style=\"color: red;\">已對示威者做出重大讓步</span>, 要同意香港爭取政改的訴求, <span style=\"color: red;\">相信習近平不會再讓步</span>."},{"pid":"6d6a3a98923017e5ac8429c1c731245cd1d706b5","tid":1298479,"uid":522,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T01:47:45.000Z","msg":"5大訴求 一樣都無"},{"pid":"23d4072b4cc52ddcaf2d7d3f8025d924f11734df","tid":1298479,"uid":215876,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T01:48:24.000Z","msg":"香港人都無步好讓"},{"pid":"ea3a71bd872f1c7cf97544693115939e597eaa43","tid":1298479,"uid":49588,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T01:52:29.000Z","msg":"香港根據基本法，早就應該有雙普選及真普選。<br />\n請中國大陸不要干涉香港內政，及不要違反香港法律。"},{"pid":"ee97f0a473025e1fba619d09c11dda2bf1712af3","tid":1298479,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T03:15:17.000Z","msg":"我無嘢講"},{"pid":"e8c42e9c79917bbfed0da6bbdaf94c375a48b58a","tid":1298479,"uid":261852,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T03:48:02.000Z","msg":"話之佢讓唔讓步, 香港人權係香港人自己嘅!!!"},{"pid":"e6fca8a85a650736566f4bc84231de462133c480","tid":1298479,"uid":155095,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T06:45:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gn3UaT0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fgn3UaT0.png&h=cb2ef61a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"02bdec0037ff378eff6f60f1b00bd447b4bf5715","tid":1298479,"uid":148332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T06:51:44.000Z","msg":"唔好講到習近平皇恩浩蕩咁啦,200萬人出黎,差不多人口3份1,佢有得唔讓咩?<br />\n就係因為普通市民睇到自己太卑微,所以先會有「唔好得罪上面」既講法"},{"pid":"f917e0edba590101943143412b6c45b2d3594870","tid":1298479,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T04:30:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://whatsticker.online/stickers_asset/ws-pack-1801056yXlhN2/200200f6bed6ff9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwhatsticker.online%2Fstickers_asset%2Fws-pack-1801056yXlhN2%2F200200f6bed6ff9.png&h=f61ceff9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"28bef4f319095a0632850a11ba1cf85dc4da8537","tid":1298479,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T10:18:43.000Z","msg":"push"}]}